  m_text: 'You are the Glades Overseer.


    You have 4 explorers and 15 days to
    gather Intel on the Maze.


    Choose who to send in, decide how your expedition
    should act when faced with the perils of the Maze.


    Decide when to call
    back your expeditioners, staying the night will most likely result in death.'
